foodOne.name: Treecheese of Heroes
foodOne.info: When re united, parmesan, cheddar and italian pecorino will grant the holder of this burger a wish!

foodTwo.name: Super Burger Bros
foodTwo.info: Italian Cheese, double ground beef and salty bacon will make you jump on a thousand turtles!

foodThree.name: Radish Quest
foodThree.info: Feel the bitter taste of battle! Conquer a monstrosity of beef with a bed of healthy purple grass!

foodFour.name: Super Smash Nachos
foodFour.info: The real battle royale awaits in your dish, where crispy nachos and great cheese vie for your attention!

foodFive.name: Chocobo Nuggets
foodFive.info: No real chocobo has been harmed in the making of these, as long you are fine with chicken...

foodSix.name: Super Fries 64
foodSix.info: Believe it or not there is no pun in this one,the fact is that it's just 64 fries for serving.
